01:09:04.760 --> 01:09:08.820 align:middle line:84%
In this way, the
prodigal child can

01:09:08.820 --> 01:09:15.499 align:middle line:84%
remember why you left the
divine world which was your home

01:09:15.499 --> 01:09:23.387 align:middle line:84%
and is your home to
which you will return.

01:09:23.387 --> 01:09:25.852 align:middle line:90%
When this journey is over.

01:09:25.852 --> 01:09:35.250 align:middle line:90%


01:09:35.250 --> 01:09:36.925 align:middle line:84%
So bring that
knowing and feeling

01:09:36.925 --> 01:09:44.118 align:middle line:84%
and sensing of
your soul's vision

01:09:44.118 --> 01:09:49.108 align:middle line:84%
into your present
sense of who you are.

01:09:49.108 --> 01:09:51.104 align:middle line:90%
Into the here now place.

01:09:51.104 --> 01:09:54.098 align:middle line:90%


01:09:54.098 --> 01:10:01.084 align:middle line:84%
Here we are on a May
Day in New York City.

01:10:01.084 --> 01:10:04.577 align:middle line:90%
In this gathering of seekers.

01:10:04.577 --> 01:10:07.072 align:middle line:90%
In this body.

01:10:07.072 --> 01:10:11.064 align:middle line:84%
These arms and legs,
these hands and feet.

01:10:11.064 --> 01:10:49.100 align:middle line:90%


01:10:49.100 --> 01:10:55.910 align:middle line:84%
It can be helpful to share
the visions that you've

01:10:55.910 --> 01:10:56.870 align:middle line:90%
had with someone else.

01:10:56.870 --> 01:11:00.510 align:middle line:84%
But we don't need to take
the time to do that now.

01:11:00.510 --> 01:11:04.830 align:middle line:84%
I'd like to suggest
that you maybe share it

01:11:04.830 --> 01:11:06.600 align:middle line:90%
or record it at least.

01:11:06.600 --> 01:11:09.020 align:middle line:90%
Write it down.

01:11:09.020 --> 01:11:11.512 align:middle line:84%
Notes from it, anything
that came to you.

01:11:11.512 --> 01:11:15.380 align:middle line:84%
>>You spoke about
integrating the vision.

01:11:15.380 --> 01:11:17.620 align:middle line:84%
Do you have any
distinctions about how

01:11:17.620 --> 01:11:20.744 align:middle line:90%
to integrate our visions?

01:11:20.744 --> 01:11:21.910 align:middle line:90%
>>How to integrate a vision?

01:11:21.910 --> 01:11:34.810 align:middle line:90%


01:11:34.810 --> 01:11:41.080 align:middle line:84%
The intention is the crucial
factor in obtaining a vision

01:11:41.080 --> 01:11:46.931 align:middle line:84%
and obtaining healing and
moving into an altered state

01:11:46.931 --> 01:11:47.555 align:middle line:90%
for divination.

01:11:47.555 --> 01:11:50.730 align:middle line:90%


01:11:50.730 --> 01:11:52.950 align:middle line:84%
In the Harvard
project, we called

01:11:52.950 --> 01:11:55.600 align:middle line:90%
it this phrase set and setting.

01:11:55.600 --> 01:11:58.417 align:middle line:84%
That the content of an
expanded consciousness

01:11:58.417 --> 01:12:00.500 align:middle line:84%
experiences a function of
the set and the setting.

01:12:00.500 --> 01:12:01.317 align:middle line:90%
Set is intention.

01:12:01.317 --> 01:12:05.987 align:middle line:90%


01:12:05.987 --> 01:12:07.620 align:middle line:90%
Or question.

01:12:07.620 --> 01:12:08.900 align:middle line:90%
Question or intention.

01:12:08.900 --> 01:12:12.920 align:middle line:84%
Divination takes place by
questioning, getting an answer.

01:12:12.920 --> 01:12:19.220 align:middle line:84%
So then the key to
integrating is also

01:12:19.220 --> 01:12:21.305 align:middle line:84%
to have the intention
towards integration.

01:12:21.305 --> 01:12:24.150 align:middle line:90%


01:12:24.150 --> 01:12:26.250 align:middle line:90%
Because that then is the choice.

01:12:26.250 --> 01:12:30.660 align:middle line:84%
Intention determines where
you direct your attention,

01:12:30.660 --> 01:12:32.030 align:middle line:90%
doesn't it?

01:12:32.030 --> 01:12:34.750 align:middle line:84%
If you have the
intention of healing,

01:12:34.750 --> 01:12:38.170 align:middle line:84%
then that's what you're
going to attend to.

01:12:38.170 --> 01:12:40.270 align:middle line:84%
If you have the
intention, if you

01:12:40.270 --> 01:12:42.160 align:middle line:84%
have a vision you're
going to be a doctor

01:12:42.160 --> 01:12:45.337 align:middle line:84%
or you're going
to be a musician,

01:12:45.337 --> 01:12:47.420 align:middle line:84%
then you would also then
would have the intention,

01:12:47.420 --> 01:12:49.530 align:middle line:84%
well, I'm going to
make that vision.

01:12:49.530 --> 01:12:52.470 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to
realize that vision.

01:12:52.470 --> 01:12:53.630 align:middle line:90%
It would be your choice.

01:12:53.630 --> 01:12:57.830 align:middle line:84%
Vision is guidance,
but it's not commands.

01:12:57.830 --> 01:12:59.280 align:middle line:90%
It's not certain.

01:12:59.280 --> 01:13:04.056 align:middle line:84%
You still have the
choice, as we know.

01:13:04.056 --> 01:13:05.680 align:middle line:84%
The people, the gang
in the White House

01:13:05.680 --> 01:13:10.170 align:middle line:84%
is choosing not to listen to
the visions that are suggested

01:13:10.170 --> 01:13:13.050 align:middle line:90%
a different course.

01:13:13.050 --> 01:13:13.930 align:middle line:90%
People can do that.

01:13:13.930 --> 01:13:16.190 align:middle line:84%
People can choose to go
against their vision.

01:13:16.190 --> 01:13:18.680 align:middle line:84%
They can choose to commit
crimes and horrible things

01:13:18.680 --> 01:13:19.260 align:middle line:90%
that they do.

01:13:19.260 --> 01:13:22.350 align:middle line:90%


01:13:22.350 --> 01:13:25.942 align:middle line:84%
But they can also
choose otherwise.

01:13:25.942 --> 01:13:29.300 align:middle line:90%
That's what I would say to that.

01:13:29.300 --> 01:13:34.680 align:middle line:84%
>>My question is, if you
feel our defeat is necessary,

01:13:34.680 --> 01:13:38.090 align:middle line:84%
what do you do to not abandon
the current situation,

01:13:38.090 --> 01:13:41.570 align:middle line:84%
the children of this time with
the Green Earth Foundation?

01:13:41.570 --> 01:13:45.820 align:middle line:84%
What is your action
for the present?

01:13:45.820 --> 01:13:47.280 align:middle line:84%
>>I don't feel
defeat is necessary.

01:13:47.280 --> 01:13:51.260 align:middle line:90%


01:13:51.260 --> 01:13:53.930 align:middle line:84%
I accept the fact that
we will be defeated.

01:13:53.930 --> 01:13:56.460 align:middle line:90%


01:13:56.460 --> 01:13:57.722 align:middle line:90%
I acknowledge that fact.

01:13:57.722 --> 01:14:00.950 align:middle line:90%


01:14:00.950 --> 01:14:09.710 align:middle line:84%
And that fact frees me
up from worrying about

01:14:09.710 --> 01:14:15.680 align:middle line:84%
whether what I do will
make any difference.

01:14:15.680 --> 01:14:22.790 align:middle line:84%
It allows me to focus on doing
what my vision tells me to do,

01:14:22.790 --> 01:14:26.430 align:middle line:84%
which is preserve life as
much as possible and those

01:14:26.430 --> 01:14:29.220 align:middle line:84%
of my children and those of the
people I come into contact with

01:14:29.220 --> 01:14:31.341 align:middle line:90%
and life, non-human life.

01:14:31.341 --> 01:14:40.930 align:middle line:90%


01:14:40.930 --> 01:14:43.400 align:middle line:84%
It's hard for people to get
that thing about defeat.

01:14:43.400 --> 01:14:48.320 align:middle line:84%
Because we're living in a part
of the globe that's doing OK.

01:14:48.320 --> 01:14:52.490 align:middle line:84%
But we could be living on a dump
heap, a trash heap in Manila

01:14:52.490 --> 01:14:54.580 align:middle line:84%
where 10,000 families
are trying to raise

01:14:54.580 --> 01:14:57.170 align:middle line:90%
their children on a trash heap.

01:14:57.170 --> 01:14:59.860 align:middle line:90%
Now, is that civilization?

01:14:59.860 --> 01:15:03.450 align:middle line:84%
Or is that a collapse
of civilization.

01:15:03.450 --> 01:15:08.480 align:middle line:90%


01:15:08.480 --> 01:15:12.920 align:middle line:90%
Does that answer your question?

01:15:12.920 --> 01:15:16.240 align:middle line:84%
>>How can you peel away
the levels of the self

01:15:16.240 --> 01:15:18.810 align:middle line:84%
and become more
authentic and real

01:15:18.810 --> 01:15:22.888 align:middle line:84%
and yet still develop your ego
in a healthy, authentic way?

01:15:22.888 --> 01:15:28.199 align:middle line:90%


01:15:28.199 --> 01:15:30.115 align:middle line:84%
>>That's one of those
psychological questions.

01:15:30.115 --> 01:15:31.805 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:15:31.805 --> 01:15:33.394 align:middle line:90%


01:15:33.394 --> 01:15:34.435 align:middle line:90%
If I were a psychologist.

01:15:34.435 --> 01:15:39.830 align:middle line:90%


01:15:39.830 --> 01:15:43.220 align:middle line:90%
It's a complicated question.

01:15:43.220 --> 01:15:47.140 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if I
have any easy answers.

01:15:47.140 --> 01:15:49.960 align:middle line:84%
The question, as I
understand it, is about well,

01:15:49.960 --> 01:15:52.912 align:middle line:84%
psychologists say you have to
develop strong ego boundaries.

01:15:52.912 --> 01:15:55.120 align:middle line:84%
And then you have these
people called borderlines who

01:15:55.120 --> 01:15:56.850 align:middle line:90%
don't have any ego boundaries.

01:15:56.850 --> 01:15:59.660 align:middle line:84%
But then I'm talking about
having a vision and expanded

01:15:59.660 --> 01:16:00.940 align:middle line:90%
sense of self.

01:16:00.940 --> 01:16:03.084 align:middle line:84%
Isn't that going in
the opposite direction?

01:16:03.084 --> 01:16:04.750 align:middle line:84%
And some psychiatrists
and psychologists

01:16:04.750 --> 01:16:06.472 align:middle line:90%
have actually written that.

01:16:06.472 --> 01:16:08.430 align:middle line:84%
And they said, well,
people who have borderline

01:16:08.430 --> 01:16:10.680 align:middle line:84%
shouldn't practice
mystical practices.

01:16:10.680 --> 01:16:12.540 align:middle line:90%
And that may be true.

01:16:12.540 --> 01:16:13.550 align:middle line:90%
I don't know.

01:16:13.550 --> 01:16:14.820 align:middle line:90%
That may be true.

01:16:14.820 --> 01:16:17.510 align:middle line:84%
>>In another words,
with taking drugs,

01:16:17.510 --> 01:16:24.181 align:middle line:84%
a borderline taking drugs,
that would be self-destructive?

01:16:24.181 --> 01:16:24.680 align:middle line:90%
>>Yeah.

01:16:24.680 --> 01:16:28.220 align:middle line:84%
But then so are a lot of
other things that people do.

01:16:28.220 --> 01:16:31.034 align:middle line:84%
And maybe it could
help sometimes.

01:16:31.034 --> 01:16:32.950 align:middle line:84%
See, it all depends on
the set and the setting

01:16:32.950 --> 01:16:34.500 align:middle line:90%
and the inclinations.

01:16:34.500 --> 01:16:39.180 align:middle line:84%
I'm very disinclined to make
general rules for people.

01:16:39.180 --> 01:16:41.080 align:middle line:84%
As somebody who
works with people,

01:16:41.080 --> 01:16:43.600 align:middle line:84%
all I go with is
somebody comes to me

01:16:43.600 --> 01:16:45.970 align:middle line:84%
and says they would
like help in something.

01:16:45.970 --> 01:16:47.560 align:middle line:90%
Then I try to address that.

01:16:47.560 --> 01:16:50.740 align:middle line:84%
I'm not really interested
in building up a system

01:16:50.740 --> 01:16:53.740 align:middle line:90%
or making generalities.

01:16:53.740 --> 01:16:57.740 align:middle line:84%
And all the things I say,
I don't really expect you

01:16:57.740 --> 01:17:00.590 align:middle line:84%
to or even want you to really
believe them or take them

01:17:00.590 --> 01:17:02.254 align:middle line:90%
on faith because I've said them.

01:17:02.254 --> 01:17:03.920 align:middle line:84%
They're like observations
that I've made

01:17:03.920 --> 01:17:05.290 align:middle line:90%
and they may be true for you.

01:17:05.290 --> 01:17:07.940 align:middle line:90%


01:17:07.940 --> 01:17:08.740 align:middle line:90%
Maybe.

01:17:08.740 --> 01:17:10.450 align:middle line:90%
And that's for you to find out.

01:17:10.450 --> 01:17:11.180 align:middle line:90%
That's for you.

01:17:11.180 --> 01:17:13.880 align:middle line:90%


01:17:13.880 --> 01:17:17.630 align:middle line:84%
So I would be reluctant
to say to people,

01:17:17.630 --> 01:17:20.560 align:middle line:90%
doing that is destructive.

01:17:20.560 --> 01:17:23.560 align:middle line:84%
But if I encountered
a particular person,

01:17:23.560 --> 01:17:26.740 align:middle line:84%
and I have said that to some
people that I've worked with,

01:17:26.740 --> 01:17:29.270 align:middle line:84%
I don't think it's a good idea
for you to be taking drugs.

01:17:29.270 --> 01:17:32.000 align:middle line:90%


01:17:32.000 --> 01:17:33.430 align:middle line:84%
Basically it's
still that choice.

01:17:33.430 --> 01:17:34.846 align:middle line:90%
And you have to respect that.

01:17:34.846 --> 01:17:37.820 align:middle line:90%


01:17:37.820 --> 01:17:41.160 align:middle line:84%
I don't believe that
teachings if you often

01:17:41.160 --> 01:17:43.660 align:middle line:84%
hear that you have
to kill the ego

01:17:43.660 --> 01:17:47.680 align:middle line:84%
and you have to overcome the
ego in order to become mystical

01:17:47.680 --> 01:17:49.080 align:middle line:90%
or spiritual.

01:17:49.080 --> 01:17:51.090 align:middle line:90%
I think that's nonsense.

01:17:51.090 --> 01:17:54.890 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the ego
is like your hand.

01:17:54.890 --> 01:17:56.570 align:middle line:90%
Actually, there are many egos.

01:17:56.570 --> 01:17:58.022 align:middle line:90%
The hand is one.

01:17:58.022 --> 01:17:59.030 align:middle line:90%
Hand has an ego.

01:17:59.030 --> 01:18:01.404 align:middle line:84%
The eye has another ego,
the heart has an ego,

01:18:01.404 --> 01:18:02.320 align:middle line:90%
the genitals have ego.

01:18:02.320 --> 01:18:07.170 align:middle line:90%


01:18:07.170 --> 01:18:11.480 align:middle line:84%
[INAUDIBLE] said
every atom has an ego.

01:18:11.480 --> 01:18:13.850 align:middle line:84%
I mean, how many atoms
are there in a body?

01:18:13.850 --> 01:18:17.110 align:middle line:90%
That's billions and trillions.

01:18:17.110 --> 01:18:20.100 align:middle line:84%
So you don't want to
chop off your hand.

01:18:20.100 --> 01:18:21.680 align:middle line:90%
That's ridiculous.

01:18:21.680 --> 01:18:24.980 align:middle line:84%
But on the other hand,
the truth in that saying

01:18:24.980 --> 01:18:30.910 align:middle line:84%
is you want your hand to be
functioning under your control

01:18:30.910 --> 01:18:32.570 align:middle line:90%
how you choose.

01:18:32.570 --> 01:18:35.597 align:middle line:84%
Not your hand to be doing
its own thing, which is

01:18:35.597 --> 01:18:36.430 align:middle line:90%
called manipulation.

01:18:36.430 --> 01:18:41.230 align:middle line:90%


01:18:41.230 --> 01:18:44.040 align:middle line:90%
Good question though, thank you.

01:18:44.040 --> 01:18:46.860 align:middle line:90%
Well, it's 11:15.

01:18:46.860 --> 01:18:48.960 align:middle line:90%
So I think I should end.

01:18:48.960 --> 01:18:51.657 align:middle line:84%
But I want to end with a
poem, a visionary column.

01:18:51.657 --> 01:18:56.750 align:middle line:84%
A short one by D.
H. Lawrence, which

01:18:56.750 --> 01:19:01.880 align:middle line:84%
is about the relationship
between individual visionary

01:19:01.880 --> 01:19:11.864 align:middle line:84%
experience and the collective
madness of our social system.

01:19:11.864 --> 01:19:16.590 align:middle line:90%


01:19:16.590 --> 01:19:19.752 align:middle line:84%
"When we get out of the
glass bottles of our ego.

01:19:19.752 --> 01:19:23.060 align:middle line:90%


01:19:23.060 --> 01:19:26.620 align:middle line:84%
When we get out of the
glass bottles of our ego

01:19:26.620 --> 01:19:29.370 align:middle line:84%
and when we escape
like squirrels turning

01:19:29.370 --> 01:19:36.000 align:middle line:84%
in the cages of our personality
and get into the forests again,

01:19:36.000 --> 01:19:38.358 align:middle line:84%
we shall shiver with
cold and fright.

01:19:38.358 --> 01:19:41.262 align:middle line:90%


01:19:41.262 --> 01:19:45.600 align:middle line:84%
But things will happen to us so
that we don't know ourselves.

01:19:45.600 --> 01:19:48.310 align:middle line:90%


01:19:48.310 --> 01:19:54.010 align:middle line:84%
Cool, unlying life will rush
in, and passion will make

01:19:54.010 --> 01:19:56.990 align:middle line:90%
our bodies taut with power.

01:19:56.990 --> 01:20:00.400 align:middle line:84%
We shall stamp our
feet with new power

01:20:00.400 --> 01:20:03.620 align:middle line:90%
and old things will fall down.

01:20:03.620 --> 01:20:12.280 align:middle line:84%
We shall laugh and institutions
will curl up like burnt paper."

01:20:12.280 --> 01:20:13.780 align:middle line:90%
So thank you very much.

01:20:13.780 --> 01:20:17.130 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:20:17.130 --> 01:21:03.034 align:middle line:90%